properties.description: Detour #10: Marathon (miles 17 + 18) and Half Marathon (mile 4 + 5): Chinatown and getting into Alameda From 8:45am to 12:40pm: To travel southbound, take 8th Street, left on Broadway, follow signs to I-880 southbound or Webster Street tube to Alameda. Or to get northbound, 8th Street, right on Brush, left onto I-980 eastbound After 12:45pm: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
